C%20if%20successful%2C%20could%20support%20some%20of%20Amazon's%20other%20goals.%20The%20project%20gets%20its%20name%20from%20the%20Kuiper%20Belt%2C%20a%20part%20of%20the%20solar%20system%20past%20the%20eight%20major%20planets.%20Kuiper%20has%20secured%20launches%20from%20various%20aerospace%20companies%2C%20including%20Blue%20Origin%2C%20which%20is%20owned%20by%20Bezos%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon's%3C%2Fa%3E%20founder%20and%20executive%20chairman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20everything%20to%20know%20about%20Project%20Kuiper's%20founding%2C%20operations%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-project-kuiper-satellites-jeff-bezos-elon-musk-starlink-spacex-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompetition%20with%20Starlink%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222a3614fe-44c2-4421-a4a0-6b5ec6feb263%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EProject%20Kuiper's%20founding%20and%20technology%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKuiper%20promises%20to%20bring%20broadband%20internet%20access%20to%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20people%2C%20especially%20those%20in%20underserved%20areas%2C%20Amazon%20says.%20The%20company%20says%20its%20services%20will%20help%20close%20the%20digital%20divide%2C%20since%20satellite%20internet%20brings%20faster%20connections%20to%20rural%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20plans%20to%20eventually%20launch%20more%20than%203%2C200%20satellites%20through%20Kuiper%2C%20which%20is%20based%20out%20of%20Washington.%20Kuiper%20has%20three%20primary%20components%2C%20according%20to%20Amazon%3A%20infrastructure%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20satellites%2C%20and%20customer%20terminals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGround%20infrastructure%20links%20the%20satellite%20network%20and%20the%20internet.%20The%20satellites%2C%20which%20sit%20in%20low%20orbit%2C%20transmit%20data%20between%20the%20ground%20infrastructure%20and%20users.%20Each%20user%20installs%20an%20outdoor%20antenna%2C%20or%20a%20%26quot%3Bcustomer%20terminal%2C%26quot%3B%20that%20connects%20to%20the%20satellite%20and%20delivers%20WiFi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKuiper%20will%20work%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faws%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Web%20Services%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20company's%20cloud%20business%20and%20the%20base%20of%20its%20profits.%20The%20ground%20services%20will%20connect%20with%20AWS%2C%20meaning%20Amazon%20could%20own%20all%20of%20the%20infrastructure%20from%20the%20server%20to%20the%20satellite%20in%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Espace%20and%20have%20more%20control%20over%20pricing%2C%20quality%2C%20and%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20AWS%20%E2%80%94%20Kuiper%20also%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20work%20with%20and%20boost%20other%20Amazon%20services.%20Alexa%2C%20for%20example%2C%20relies%20on%20an%20internet%20connection.%20Kuiper%20could%20bring%20the%20voice%20assistant%20to%20people%20who%20currently%20lack%20internet.%20The%20same%20goes%20for%20bringing%20the%20internet%20to%20new%20potential%20Amazon%20Prime%20members%20and%20general%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ee6265b6-3fdf-41d9-aa1d-39cae7783195%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETimeline%20and%20launch%20plans%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20began%20researching%20Kuiper%20in%202018%2C%20and%20the%20Federal%20Communications%20Commission%20gave%20the%20company%20a%20license%20to%20start%20sending%20satellites%20to%20space%20in%20July%202020.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-delays-project-kuiper-satellite-launch-after-switching-rockets-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKuiper's%20initial%20launch%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20prototype%20satellites%20was%20scheduled%20for%20late%202022%20but%20was%20delayed%20when%20Amazon%20changed%20the%20rocket-delivery%20system.%20Eventually%2C%20Amazon%20sent%20its%20first%20two%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-launches-first-satellites-to-challenge-elon-musk-starlink-spacex-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKuiper%20prototype%20satellites%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20orbit%20in%20October%20of%202023.%20Those%20satellites%20were%20used%20to%20test%20parts%20of%20the%20Kuiper%20system%20before%20deploying%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20whole%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20April%2028%2C%202025%2C%20Amazon%20launched%2027%20satellites%20and%20the%20company%20said%20it%20had%20established%20communications%20with%20all%20of%20them.%20A%20rocket%20from%20United%20Launch%20Alliance%2C%20a%20joint%20venture%20Boeing%20and%20Lockheed%20Martin%2C%20sent%20the%20satellites%20into%20space.%20Amazon%20said%20it%20has%20secured%20more%20than%2080%20launches%20with%20a%20range%20of%20rocket%20companies%20in%20addition%20to%20ULA%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblue-origin%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBlue%20Origin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20SpaceX%2C%20and%20the%20French%20company%20Arianespace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20approved%20Kuiper's%20plans%2C%20the%20FCC%20said%20Amazon%20needs%20to%20deploy%20at%20least%20half%20of%20its%20satellites%20by%20the%20end%20of%20July%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKuiper%20internet%20will%20become%20available%20to%20customers%20before%20the%20end%20of%202025%2C%20if%20launches%20stay%20on%20schedule%20and%20all%20goes%20to%20plan.%20The%20project%20is%20hugely%20expensive%20%E2%80%94%20Amazon%20has%20invested%20%2410%20billion%20into%20Kuiper%20%E2%80%94%20but%20could%20also%20be%20quite%20profitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20Amazon's%20core%20e-commerce%20business%2C%20which%20has%20thin%20margins%2C%20broadband%20services%20could%20have%20an%2080%25%20margin%2C%20BI%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22000116f3-0d98-4b05-8b01-176f42f6f09e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EProject%20Kuiper%20vs.%20Starlink%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBezos'%20Kuiper%20and%20Musk's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%