the%20ruling%20stays%20put%2C%20it%20means%20the%20five%20years%20and%20the%20enormous%20amount%20of%20money%20Sweeney%20says%20he%20spent%20and%20sacrificed%20by%20challenging%20Apple%20and%20its%20CEO%2C%20Tim%20Cook%2C%20will%20have%20paid%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExplaining%20why%20Apple's%20App%20Store%20rules%20are%20so%20important%20%E2%80%94%20to%20both%20Apple%20and%20the%20developers%20who%20complain%20about%20them%20%E2%80%94%20can%20be%20a%20drag%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-app-store-court-ruling-epic-game-charges-2025-5%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520a%2520nutshell%3A%2520Epic%2520doesn%2Cled%2520to%2520the%2520civil%2520suit.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethough%20I%20keep%20trying%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20wanted%20to%20hear%20Sweeney's%20take%20on%20it%20directly%20because%20he's%20made%20the%20fight%20a%20core%20part%20of%20his%20job%20for%20half%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20I%20also%20wanted%20to%20know%20when%20I'll%20be%20able%20to%20play%20Fortnite%20on%20my%20iPhone%20%E2%80%94%20something%20I%20haven't%20been%20able%20to%20do%20since%202020%2C%20when%20Sweeney%20first%20started%20fighting%20with%20Apple.%20(I've%20asked%20Apple%20for%20comment%2C%20but%20they%20haven't%20expanded%20on%20the%20statement%20they%20made%20last%20week%20expressing%20their%20disappointment%20and%20plans%20to%20appeal.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20hear%20our%20entire%20discussion%20over%20on%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpodcasts.apple.com%2Fus%2Fpodcast%2Fchannels-with-peter-kafka%2Fid1080467174%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChannels%3C%2Fa%3E%20podcast.%20The%20following%20is%20an%20edited%20excerpt%20of%20our%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPeter%20Kafka%3A%20Why%20was%20last%20week's%20ruling%20important%20to%20you%20and%20Epic%3F%20And%20why%20should%20a%20normal%20person%20care%20about%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETim%20Sweeney%3A%20This%20is%20really%20one%20of%20the%20issues%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20our%20digital%20freedoms%20for%20the%20future.%20We%20live%20our%20lives%20on%20our%20smartphones.%20We're%20connected%20constantly%20to%20people.%20We%20work%20on%20them.%20We%20play%20on%20them.%20And%20our%20futures%20are%20going%20to%20be%20ever%20more%20connected%20there.%20So%20the%20freedom%20for%20consumers%20and%20developers%20to%20do%20business%20together%20is%20of%20paramount%20importance.%20If%20you%20have%20one%20monopoly%20gatekeeper%20who%20dictates%20what%20people%20are%20allowed%20to%20play%2C%20see%2C%20hear%20%E2%80%94%20and%20takes%20exorbitant%20fees%20from%20every%20transaction%20that%20everybody%20does%20online%20%E2%80%94%20we're%20going%20to%20have%20a%20much%20less%20free%20world%20than%20the%20one%20that%20we%20grew%20up%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20programming%20back%20on%20an%20Apple%20II%20when%20I%20was%2013%3A%20You%20turn%20the%20computer%20on%2C%20you%20get%20a%20BASIC%20programming%20prompt.%20Anybody%20can%20write%20code%2C%20anybody%20can%20save%20it%20to%20a%20floppy%20disk%2C%20you%20can%20share%20it%20with%20a%20friend%2C%20you%20can%20sell%20it.%20Those%20digital%20freedoms%20are%20essential%20to%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20subscribe%20to%20Netflix.%20I%20subscribe%20to%20Spotify.%20Neither%20of%20those%20is%20done%20through%20Apple%20because%20in%20both%20cases%2C%20neither%20of%20those%20companies%20wanted%20to%20pay%20Apple's%20fees.%20But%20I%20use%20Spotify%20and%20Netflix%20on%20my%20phone.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20could%20maybe%20argue%20that%20it's%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20hassle%20for%20me%20to%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20Netflix%20on%20a%20website%20instead%20of%20directly%20through%20its%20iOS%20app.%20But%20it%20doesn't%20really%20seem%20like%20it's%20a%20sort%20of%20life%20and%20death%20situation%20for%20me%20or%20any%20of%20the%20companies%20involved.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20has%20two%20tiers%20of%20rules.%20They%20have%20one%20tier%20of%20rules%20for%20what%20they%20call%20reader%20apps%2C%20which%20are%20basically%20apps%20operated%20by%20multi-hundred-billion-dollar%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20Amazon%20Video%2C%20Netflix%2C%20Spotify%2C%20and%20a%20number%20of%20others.%20Apple%20lets%20those%20apps%20do%20business%20outside%20of%20the%20app.%20And%20they've%20previously%20obstructed%20those%20developers%20from%20telling%20users%20about%20the%20better%20deals%20%5Byou%20could%20get%20by%20going%20to%20those%20sites%20directly%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20even%20with%20that%20restriction%2C%20which%20is%20now%20being%20taken%20away%2C%20it%20seemed%20like%20life%20was%20OK%20for%20me%2C%20life%20was%20OK%20for%20Netflix%2C%20life%20was%20OK%20for%20Apple.%20Everyone%20was%20getting%20what%20they%20wanted.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20%3Cem%3Enot%3C%2Fem%3E%20OK%20for%20game%20developers.%20Because%20that%20reader%20app%20exception%20only%20applied%20to%20streaming%20video%2C%20streaming%20audio%2C%20and%20ebook%20sites.%20Apple%20forced%20all%20games%2C%20all%20social%20media%20apps%2C%20and%20everything%20else%2C%20to%20only%20do%20business%20through%20their%20app.%20So%20Apple%20imposed%20a%20rule%20on%20all%20game%20developers%2C%20saying%20if%20you%20sell%20anything%20for%20your%20game%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20on%20any%20platform%2C%20then%20you%20must%20sell%20it%20on%20iOS%2C%20and%20you%20must%20use%20our%20payment%20method%2C%20and%20you%20must%20pay%20us%2030%25%20if%20your%20revenue%20is%20greater%20than%20a%20million%20dollars.%20So%20the%20game%20developers%20did%20not%20have%20a%20choice%2C%20and%20everything%20there%20was%20just%20marked%20up%2030%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happens%20given%20the%20ruling%20last%20week%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20means%20now%20all%20users%20are%20free%20to%20learn%20about%20better%20deals%20from%20all%20developers%2C%20and%20all%20developers%20are%20free%20to%20not%20just%20accept%20payments%20outside%20of%20the%20app%20on%20the%20web%2C%20but%20to%20tell%20users%20about%20those%20alternative%20ways%20to%20pay%20and%20to%20give%20consumers%20better%20deals.%20That's%20a%20key%20economic%20gain%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20developers%20will%20be%20able%20to%20send%20users%20to%20the%20web%20to%20give%20them%20a%20better%20price%2C%20and%20then%20to%20make%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20money%20for%20themselves%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that's%20just%20the%20first-order%20effect.%20The%20second-order%20effect%20is%20that%20you%20can%20expect%20if%20Apple%20continues%20to%20offer%20such%20a%20horrible%20deal%2C%20that%20everybody's%20going%20to%20move%20away%20and%20steer%20their%20customers%20towards%20iOS%20payments%20on%20the%20web.%20So%20I%20would%20hope%20that%20Apple%20would%20step%20up%20and%20compete%2C%20give%20developers%20a%20much%20better%20deal%20than%2030%25%2C%20and%20actually%20engage%20in%20competition.%20But%20whether%20Apple%20chooses%20to%20compete%20or%20not%2C%20the%20court%20has%20enabled%20developers%20to%20make%20the%20choice%20for%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EApple%20says%20they're%20going%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20judge's%20ruling%2C%20but%20they're%20also%20going%20to%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2Fnews%2F661032%2Fapple-epic-games-app-store-antitrust-ninth-circuit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Eappeal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20it.%20So%20it's%20possible%20the%20rules%20get%20changed%20again.%20Do%20you%20think%20a%20meaningful%20number%20of%20developers%20are%20willing%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20this%20window%2C%20knowing%20that%20it%20can%20get%20shut%20down%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%2030%25%20of%20revenue%2C%20so%20all%20major%20developers%20will%20support%20alternative%20payments.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2025%2F05%2F02%2Fapple-approves-spotify-app-update-that-allows-u-s-users-to-access-pricing-info-external-payment-links%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpotify%20was%20the%20first%20major%20app%20I%20saw%20that%20already%20has%20done%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Fortnite%20will%20do%20it%20later%20this%20week.%20And%20many%2C%20many%20apps%20are%20doing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20said%20Fortnite%20is%20going%20to%20come%20back%20to%20iOS.%20You%20guys%20were%20kicked%20off%20the%20platform%20in%202020%20for%20violating%20Apple's%20rules.%20There's%20nothing%20in%20the%20judge's%20ruling%20that%20says%20Apple%20has%20to%20reinstate%20Fortnite%20on%20iOS.%20Have%20you%20talked%20to%20Apple%3F%20How%20do%20you%20imagine%20Fortnite%20will%20come%20back%20to%20iOS%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEpic%20has%20a%20valid%20%5BApple%5D%20developer%20account%20in%20good%20standing.%20Our%20subsidiary%20Epic%20Games%20Sweden%20opened%20up%20an%20account%20in%20order%20to%20distribute%20Fortnite%20in%20the%20European%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20dealings%20with%20Apple%20on%20that%20account%20have%20been%20managed%20by%20their%20developer%20relations%20team%2C%20who%20have%20been%20cordial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20feel%20confident%20that%20I%20will%20be%20able%20to%20play%20Fortnite%20on%20my%20iPhone%20later%20this%20week%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20believe%20so.%20I%20would%20be%20very%20surprised%20%E2%80%94%20well%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20terribly%20surprised%20if%20we%20had%20a%20bug%20that%20took%20a%20day%20or%20two%20more%20to%20fix%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20would%20be%20very%20surprised%20if%20Apple%20decided%20to%20brave%20the%20geopolitical%20storm%20of%20blocking%20a%20major%20app%20from%20iOS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20told%20Apple%20what%20we're%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20much%20has%20it%20cost%20you%20to%20engage%20in%20this%20five-year%20legal%20fight%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20had%20legal%20bills%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20Epic%20vs.%20Apple%20of%20over%20%24100%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20assumed%20it%20was%20much%20more.%20You%20were%20hiring%20top-shelf%20lawyers%20and%20%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20yeah.%20Well%20over%20%24100%20million%2C%20just%20in%20legal%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20you%20look%20at%20lost%20revenue%2C%20that's%20another%20story.%20We%20can't%20predict%20exactly%20how%20much%20we%20would%20have%20made%20on%20iOS%2C%20but%20in%20the%20two%20years%20that%20we%20were%20on%20the%20platform%2C%20Fortnite%20had%20made%20about%20%24300%20million%20on%20iOS.%20So%20you%20could%20have%20projected%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20of%20lost%20revenue%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20that's%20just%20from%20people%20who%20were%20playing%20and%20couldn't%20play.%20I'm%20thinking%20of%20the%20future%20players%20you%20would%20have%20gotten%2C%20who%20didn't%20get%20exposed%20to%20the%20game%20because%20they%20don't%20have%20access%20to%20it%20via%20their%20phone.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froblox-games-ceo-parents-kids-rules-responsible-age-moderation-2025-04%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERoblox%20has%20tons%20of%20young%20players.%20The%20majority%20there%20are%20teenagers%20or%20below%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E.%20They're%20all%20getting%20to%20it%20via%20their%20phone.%20Those%20are%20all%20people%20who%20could%20have%20played%20Fortnite%20for%20the%20last%20five%20years.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20right.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FMetcalfe%2527s_law%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMetcalfe%2527s%2520law%2520characterizes%2520many%2520of%2Cservice%2520becomes%2520to%2520the%2520community.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMetcalfe's%20Law%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20real%20factor%20here.%20You're%20much%20more%20likely%20to%20play%20a%20game%20or%20use%20a%20social%20network%20if%20your%20friends%20are%20there.%20So%20Apple%20cutting%20off%20Epic%20from%20access%20to%20the%20entire%20iOS%20audience%2C%20that%20not%20only%20affects%20the%20players%20that%20are%20directly%20denied%20access%20to%20Fortnite%2C%20it%20also%20affects%20all%20of%20their%20friends%20who%20might%20have%20played%20Fortnite%20more%20or%20might%20have%20played%20Fortnite%20but%20didn't%2C%20because%20their%20friends%20weren't%20able%20to%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20you%20could%20easily%20imagine%20that%20there's%20been%20a%20billion%20dollars%20or%20more%20of%20impact%20to%20Epic%20in%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20freedom%20cannot%20be%20purchased%20at%20too%20dear%20a%20price.%20The%20world%20needs%20to%20change%20here.%20And%20if%20it%20doesn't%20change%2C%20then%20you're%20just%20going%20to%20have%20Apple%20and%20Google%20extracting%20all%20of%20the%20profit%20from%20all%20apps%20forever.%20And%20there%20will%20be%20no%20proper%20digital%20economy.%20It%20will%20just%20be%20monopolization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20understand%20the%20logic%20and%20emotion%20behind%20that%20argument.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%3A%20You're%20running%20a%20for-profit%20company.%20You%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20investors.%20They%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20into%20you.%20Did%20they%20come%20to%20you%20at%20any%20point%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BTim%2C%20I%20know%20that%20freedom%20cannot%20be%20purchased%20at%20too%20dear%20a%20price.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20I've%20invested%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20in%20you%20because%20you're%20a%20games%20company%2C%20and%20your%20game%20is%20banned%20from%20mobile%20phones.%20Could%20you%20just%20settle%20this%20up%20and%20declare%20victory%20and%20move%20on%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20one%20investor%20who%20exited%20Epic%20right%20quick%2C%20everybody%20has%20stood%20by%20us%2C%20because%20nobody%20invested%20in%20Epic%20because%20they%20want%20to%20make%20a%2030%25%20profit%20flipping%20the%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20invested%20in%20%5Bus%5D%2C%20believe%20in%20our%20vision%2C%20believe%20in%20our%20potential%2C%20and%20believe%20that%20if%20we%20succeed%20in%20building%20the%20metaverse%20and%20growing%20Fortnite%20from%20a%20game%20into%20an%20ecosystem%2C%20into%20an%20open%20platform%20serving%20literally%20billions%20of%20players%2C%20that%20it%20will%20totally%20have%20been%20worth%20it.%20They%20all%20realize%20that%20if%20Apple%20controls%20the%20spigot%2C%20the%20revenue%20spigot%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20funnel%2C%20they%20will%20use%20that%20control%20to%20extract%20all%20of%20the%20profit%20that%20will%20ever%20be%20made%20from%20this%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20imagine%20this%20is%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20professional%20life%20%E2%80%94%20running%20a%20business%2C%20coding%2C%20and%20then%20also%20having%20legal%20fights%20with%20platforms%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20game%20and%20a%20meta%20game%20here%2C%20right%3F%20The%20game%20is%20making%20awesome%20software%2C%20which%20is%20awesomely%20fun%2C%20creatively%20and%20technically.%20I%20love%20that.%20But%20there's%20a%20meta%20game%20of%20ensuring%20that%20we%20have%20the%20right%20to%20do%20that%2C%20and%20that%20we%20can%20profit%20from%20the%20fruits%20of%20our%20labor%2C%20and%20that%20all%20developers%20can.%20So%20much%20of%20our%20business%20is%20not%20just%20Epic%20profiting%20from%20our%20games.%20It's%20Epic%20helping%20other%20developers%20succeed%20and%20profiting%20from%20the%20success%20of%20thousands%20or%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20different%20developers%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEpic%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20companies%20in%20the%20industry%20that's%20positioned%20in%20a%20way%20that%20really%20forces%20us%20to%20fight%20for%20everybody.%20And%20I%20don't%20feel%20bad%20about%20this.%20I%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20brain%20power%20into%20coding%20over%20the%20years.%20I%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20brain%20power%20into%20figuring%20out%