%20conglomerate%20that%20invested%20%2420%20billion%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20with%20another%20up%20to%20%2420%20billion%20(part%20coming%20from%20a%20syndicate)%20becoming%20available%20in%20December%20if%20it%20restructured%20as%20a%20for-profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20OpenAI%20previously%20raised%20several%20billion%20from%20other%20investors%20last%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-deadline-to-become-for-profit-or-return-investor-money-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewith%20a%20provision%3C%2Fa%3E%20allowing%20investors%20to%20claw%20back%20funds%20if%20the%20company%20had%20not%20restructured%20within%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20current%20formation%2C%20OpenAI%20is%20beholden%20to%20a%20nonprofit%20parent%20organization%20%E2%80%94%20an%20unconventional%20corporate%20structure%20that%20some%20investors%20have%20rankled%20at%2C%20and%20placed%20stipulations%20on%20their%20investments%20requiring%20it%20to%20be%20restructured%20within%20a%20specific%20timeframe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20first%20attempt%20to%20resolve%20it%20by%20severing%20the%20link%20between%20the%20for-profit%20subsidiary%20and%20the%20nonprofit%20parent%20faltered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-elon-musk-sam-altman-for-profit-conversion-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20the%20face%20of%20scrutiny%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20everyone%20from%20state%20attorneys%20general%20to%20academics%20to%20Elon%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20successful%2C%20the%20latest%20restructuring%20will%20provide%20clarity%20for%20investors%20and%20employees%2C%20also%20removing%20its%20convoluted%20%26quot%3Bcapped-profit%26quot%3B%20model%20that%20saw%20investor%20returns%20top%20out%20at%20a%20theoretical%20100x.%20And%20it%20removes%20what%20had%20the%20potential%20to%20be%20a%20catastrophic%20hurdle%20for%20OpenAI%20%E2%80%94%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20huge%20tracts%20of%20funding%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0as%20it%20faces%20intense%20competition%20from%20Anthropic%2C%20Google%2C%20Musk's%20xAI%2C%20and%20other%20rival%20AI%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOpenAI%20was%20founded%20as%20a%20nonprofit%2C%20is%20today%20a%20nonprofit%20that%20oversees%20and%20controls%20the%20for-profit%2C%20and%20going%20forward%20will%20remain%20a%20nonprofit%20that%20oversees%20and%20controls%20the%20for-profit%2C%26quot%3B%20Sam%20Altman%20wrote%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20employees%20that%20the%20company%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenai.com%2Findex%2Fevolving-our-structure%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%20publicly%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20will%20not%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aacf6d20-b5c9-4d47-83c9-c5254cb8758c%5C%22%3E'The%20devil's%20in%20the%20details'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERose%20Chan%20Loui%2C%20a%20law%20professor%20and%20expert%20in%20nonprofit%20law%20at%20UCLA%20who%20has%20previously%20been%20critical%20of%20OpenAI's%20plans%2C%20said%20she%20found%20the%20new%20proposal%20%26quot%3Bencouraging.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20saying%20all%20the%20right%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20saying%20that%20the%20mission%20remains%20the%20same%2C%20that%20the%20PBC%20will%20have%20the%20same%20mission%2C%20and%20whether%20or%20not%20that%20really%20happens%2C%20I%20think%20depends%20on%20what%20processes%20they%20set%20up%20in%20terms%20of%20governance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20cautioned%20that%20there%20are%20still%20a%20number%20of%20unanswered%20questions%2C%20including%20the%20nature%20of%20how%20the%20nonprofit%20will%20legally%20control%20and%20practically%20monitor%20the%20public%20benefit%20corporation%2C%20the%20financial%20stake%20the%20nonprofit%20will%20hold%2C%20and%20the%20governance%20structure%20of%20the%20nonprofit.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20devil's%20in%20the%20details%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobert%20Weissman%2C%20the%20co-president%20at%20Public%20Citizen%2C%20a%20public%20advocacy%20group%2C%20is%20less%20optimistic.%20Public%20Citizen%20has%20previously%20argued%20that%20OpenAI%20has%20already%20effectively%20surrendered%20its%20charitable%20mission%20in%20pursuit%20of%20for-profit%20goals%20and%20should%20be%20forced%20to%20convert%20to%20a%20for-profit%20entirely%20and%20compensate%20the%20charitable%20sector%20for%20its%20purported%20failures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20lot%20of%20ways%20it's%20saying%3A%20'we're%20going%20to%20keep%20doing%20what%20we've%20been%20doing%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%20what%20they've%20been%20doing%20is%20unacceptable%2C%20and%20fails%20to%20uphold%20their%20nonprofit%20mission.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20ongoing%20efforts%20to%20raise%20capital%2C%20he%20said%2C%20are%20indicative%20that%20the%20nonprofit%20%26quot%3Bwill%20not%20be%20exerting%20meaningful%20control%20over%20the%20now-public%20benefit%20corporation's%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20has%20to%20be%20some%20demonstration%20of%20a%20fundamental%20reorientation%20by%20the%20nonprofit%20to%20actually%20exert%20control%20and%20direct%20the%20for-profit%20in%20some%20way%20that%20reflected%20its%20nonprofit%20values.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e428279f-0494-4c47-a3e0-391caf3accc3%5C%22%3EThe%20attorneys%20general%20have%20their%20say%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20new%20structure%20is%20not%20a%20done%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20decision%20on%20whether%20OpenAI%20goes%20ahead%20with%20it%20will%20be%20made%20by%20the%20attorneys%20general%20in%20California%20and%20Delaware%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20said%20they%20planned%20to%20review%20the%20new%20proposal.%20(In%20OpenAI's%20blog%20post%2C%20board%20chair%20Bret%20Taylor%20wrote%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20made%20the%20decision%20for%20the%20nonprofit%20to%20retain%20control%20of%20OpenAI%20after%20hearing%20from%20civic%20leaders%20and%20engaging%20in%20constructive%20dialogue%20with%20the%20offices%20of%20the%20Attorney%20General%20of%20Delaware%20and%20the%20Attorney%20General%20of%20California.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20BI%2C%20Delaware%20Attorney%20General%20Kathy%20Jennings%20said%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bencouraged%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Monday%20announcement%2C%20saying%20the%20company%20is%20%26quot%3Bseeking%20to%20address%26quot%3B%20her%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20that%20the%20Company%20has%20a%20new%20plan%2C%20I%20intend%20to%20review%20it%20for%20compliance%20with%20Delaware%20law%20by%20ensuring%20that%20it%20accords%20with%20OpenAI's%20charitable%20purpose%20and%20that%20the%20non-profit%20entity%20retains%20appropriate%20control%20over%20the%20for-profit%20entity%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECalifornia%20Attorney%20General%20Rob%20Bonta%20was%20more%20terse%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20BI%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20California%20Department%20of%20Justice%20is%20reviewing%20the%20new%20proposed%20plan.%20This%20remains%20an%20ongoing%20matter%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we%20are%20in%20continued%20conversations%20with%20OpenAI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenais-new-restructure-plan-investor-requirements-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746522001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68193aeaa466d2b74ab5186d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenais-new-restructure-plan-investor-requirements-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22OpenAI%20needs%20to%20restructure%20itself%20or%20lose%20billions%20of%20dollars.%20It%20thinks%20it%20has%20a%20new%20solution.%20Experts%20are%20skeptical.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rprice%40insider.com%20(Rob%20Price)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenais-new-restru