high%20performers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wrote%20a%20final%20email%20to%20my%20skip-level%20manager%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BNot%20to%20get%20my%20job%20back.%20Not%20even%20to%20get%20a%20reply%20(I%20didn't).%20I%20just%20wanted%20to%20be%20heard.%20To%20say%3A%20I%20know%20I%20did%20good%20work.%20I%20know%20I%20didn't%20deserve%20this.%20And%20I%20hope%20someone%20%E2%80%94%20anyone%20%E2%80%94%20in%20leadership%20still%20has%20the%20humanity%20to%20care.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226897013a-c030-402f-b972-743bcb752eb4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20about%20filling%20quotas%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20employee%20spent%20four%20years%20at%20Meta%20working%20on%20internal%20security%20systems%2C%20including%20tools%20to%20manage%20insider%20threats.%20He%20spent%20the%20weekend%20before%20the%20cuts%20making%20sure%20those%20would%20run%20smoothly%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20layoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20received%20consistently%20strong%20performance%20ratings%2C%20and%20said%20his%20managers%20agreed%20he%20was%20on%20track%2C%20but%20his%20termination%20letter%20assigned%20him%20a%20%26quot%3BMeets%20Most%20Expectations%26quot%3B%20rating.%20He%20said%20his%20managers%20didn't%20look%20at%20the%20self-review%20he%20submitted.%20%26quot%3BThat%20told%20me%20everything.%20This%20wasn't%20about%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20about%20filling%20quotas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20manager%20said%20he%20'stood%20by'%20the%20rating%20but%20wished%20he'd%20had%20more%20time%20and%20freedom%20to%20talk%20things%20through.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20view%2C%20the%20company%20culture%20had%20grown%20increasingly%20cutthroat%2C%20with%20employees%20clinging%20to%20projects%20to%20boost%20their%20ratings%2C%20jockeying%20within%20the%20performance%20curve%2C%20and%20seeing%20dissent%20increasingly%20punished.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26