ays%20his%20attitude%20has%20undergone%20a%20shift.%20%E2%80%9CWhether%20you%20qualify%20or%20not%2C%20UPSC%20changes%20your%20perspective%3B%20it%20adds%20to%20your%20personality%20and%20thinking.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManu%20remained%20committed%20to%20this%20newfound%20approach%20of%20perceiving%20the%20world.%20And%20it%20came%20to%20his%20rescue%20during%20his%20interview%20process%20at%20the%20UPSC%20CSE%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20interview%20was%20on%2027%20January%202025%20%E2%80%93%20around%20the%20time%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20took%20the%20oath%20and%20began%20implementing%20his%20policies.%20My%20interview%20focused%20on%20the%20impact%20of%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20policies%2C%20not%20just%20in%20India%20but%20on%20a%20wider%2C%20global%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20how%20President%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20control%20of%20Greenland%20would%20impact%20India%2C%20Manu%20gave%20the%20interviewers%20a%20balanced%20critique%20of%20this%20sensitive%20issue.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20just%20highlight%20the%20negative%20points%2C%20but%20also%20spoke%20about%20how%2C%20if%20India%20struck%20a%20trade%20deal%20with%20President%20Trump%2C%20it%20would%20give%20us%20an%20invaluable%20edge%20with%20other%20countries%20to%20increase%20our%20trade%20surplus.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Being%20able%20to%20handwrite%20your%20notes%20is%20a%20blessing.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20take%20it%20lightly.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20multiple%20occasions%2C%20whilst%20preparing%20for%20the%20exam%2C%20Manu%20found%20himself%20dearly%20missing%20the%20ability%20to%20make%20notes.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20realise%20how%20being%20able%20to%20just%20open%20a%20book%20and%20skim%20through%20notes%20when%20we%20want%20to%20revise%20a%20topic%2C%20helps.%20Navigating%20a%20PDF%20is%20tough.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5