%5C%22%3EThe%20EV%20Doctor%20is%20used%20in%20more%20than%201%2C700%20EV%20workshops%20and%20service%20centres%20across%20India%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20Vietnam%2C%20Mexico%2C%20Mauritius%2C%20and%20the%20United%20States%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20first%20glance%2C%20EV%20Doctor%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20simple%20device.%20But%20inside%20its%20300-gram%20frame%20lies%20a%20powerful%20system%20built%20around%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20years%20of%20battery-specific%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTraditional%20battery%20testing%20relies%20heavily%20on%20charge-discharge%20cyclers%2C%20or%20CDC%20machines%2C%20which%20are%20bulky%20systems%20that%20take%20seven%20to%20eight%20hours%20to%20provide%20basic%20statistics%20like%20voltage%20and%20capacity.%20These%20metrics%20alone%20are%20insufficient%20for%20diagnosing%20deeper%20battery%20issues%20such%20as%20internal%20resistance%20or%20early-stage%20safety%20faults%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Shubham.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEV%20Doctor%20changed%20the%20game.%20Instead%20of%20taking%20hours%20to%20test%20a%20battery%20like%20traditional%20machines%2C%20it%20uses%20smart%20technology%20to%20check%20everything%20in%20just%2015%20minutes.%20It%20looks%20at%20how%20the%20battery%20behaves%20when%20electricity%20flows%20through%20it%20and%20uses%20over%2025%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F406804%2Fifs-varun-jain-ai-human-elephant-conflict-chhattisgarh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20understand%20its%20overall%20health%2C%20safety%2C%20performance%2C%20and%20faults.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20device%20works%20with%20all%20kinds%20of%20batteries%2C%20whether%20they%20use%20advanced%20communication%20systems%20like%20Controller%20Area%20Network%20(CAN)%20or%20not%2C%20and%20can%20test%20batteries%20up%20to%20100%20volts%20and%20100%20ampere-hours%20in%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBattery%20tests%20that%20take%20minutes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20a%20user%20has%20to%20do%20is%20connect%20the%20device%20to%20a%20battery%20and%20charger.%20It%20then%20transmits%20real-time%20data%20%E2%80%93%20like%20voltage%2C%20current%2C%20and%20time%2C%20to%20cloud-based%20algorithms%20that%20compute%20safety%20parameters%2C%20fault%20detection%2C%20and%20capacity%20degradation.%20The%20results%20are%20sent%20back%20to%20a%20mobile%20app%20with%20a%20complete%20report%20on%20the%20battery%E2%80%99s%20health%2C%20safety%2C%20performance%2C%20and%20faults%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T215409.995_11zon-1746030266.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20EV%20Doctor%20device%20has%20been%20tested%20on%20over%20five%20lakh%20batteries%20so%20far%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T215409.995_11zon-1746030266.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T215409.995_11zon-1746030266-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T215409.995_11zon-1746030266-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T215409.995_11zon-1746030266-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Bus