%20and%20in%20August%2C%20he%20officially%20registered%20his%20startup%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fin.linkedin.com%2Fcompany%2Faltersage-innovations%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAltersage%20Innovations%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20the%20dream%20team%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Ashin%20needed%20a%20team%20to%20bring%20his%20vision%20to%20life.%20So%20in%202023%2C%20he%20circulated%20posters%20calling%20for%20interns%2C%20eventually%20filtering%20down%20from%2015%20candidates%20to%20a%20tight-knit%20group.%20Today%2C%20his%20team%20of%20four%20works%20out%20of%20a%20small%20office%20in%20Kozhikode%2C%20focusing%20on%20refining%20the%20prototype%20into%20a%20minimum%20viable%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20invention%2C%20Coco-bot%2C%20is%20a%20compact%2C%20semi-automatic%20robot%20that%20weighs%20under%2010%20kgs%20and%20can%20be%20easily%20fixed%20onto%20any%20coconut%20tree.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20height%20is%20similar%20to%20a%20gaming%20laptop.%20One%20person%20can%20carry%20it%20and%20fix%20it%20onto%20the%20tree%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ashin%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-30T185509.862-1746019533.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20team%20behind%20Coco-bot%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-30T185509.862-1746019533.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-30T185509.862-1746019533-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-30T185509.862-1746019533-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-30T185509.862-1746019533-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-30T185509.862-1746019533-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-424337%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20team%20behind%20bringing%20Coco-bot%20to%20life.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20climbs%20as%20fast%20as%20a%20human%2C%20and%20once%20at%20the%20top%2C%20its%20in-house%20developed%20wireless%20robotic%20arm%20harvests%20coconuts%20and%20leaves%20and%20even%20performs%20maintenance.%20It%20is%20controlled%20through%20a%20custom-built%20console.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20console%20is%20not%20complicated%20to%20operate%20and%20can%20be%20easily%20learned%20within%20a%20span%20of%20two%20hours%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Gokul%20Krishan%2C%20the%20Chief%20Technical%20Officer%20(CTO)%20at%20Altersage%20Innovations%2C%20who%20has%20been%20involved%20in%20the%20company%20for%20over%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAmong%20the%20elements%2C%20building%20the%20robotic%20arm%20took%20time%2C%20as%20it%20was%20challenging%20to%20replicate%20the%20hand%20movement%20of%20a%20human%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Gokul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChanging%20the%20future%20of%20coconut%20farming%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoco-bot%20aims%20to%20revolutionise%20coconut%20farming%20by%20making%20it%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F320826%2Fbengaluru-professor-saji-varghese-makes-sunbird-straws-from-coconut-leaves-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esafer%20and%20more%20accessible%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CClimbing%20a%2020-metre%20tree%20is%20extremely%20risky%20and%20physically%20demanding%2C%E2%80%9